node.text:
Elon Musk, founder of SpaceX and CEO of Tesla always found it hard fitting in with others. But when his ex wife, Justine Wilson exposed Elon’s secret - Elon’s worst fears came boiling to the surface. He tried to escape into his work, but the dark truth was out. What’s the REAL reason behind Elon Musk’s level of ambition? And what painful lesson was he forced to finally learn?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Goalcast on August 22, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Goalcast Forgive anyone who has caused you pain. Keep in mind that forgiving is not for others. It S for you. Forgiving is not forgetting. It is remembering without anger. It frees up your power, heals your body, mind and spirit. Forgiveness opens up a pathway to a new place peace. LES BROWN'.

node.text:
Forgiveness is powerful. And though you may believe that you are doing something good to others by forgiving them, you are actually doing far more good to yourself.

Forgiving essentially frees 𝙮𝙤𝙪𝙧𝙨𝙚𝙡𝙛 from the binding effect of expecting others to acknowledge and pay for what they have done to you. By deciding to make peace with it instead of waging war against it, you pacify yourself. And you’ll feel so much better.

#lesbrown #forgivenessquotes #selflove #selfcare #selfdevelopment #mindfulness #bethebestyou #personalgrowth #growthmindset #mindsetiseverything #relationships #wellness #wellnessjourney #personaldevelopment

node.text:
Elon Musk, founder of SpaceX and CEO of Tesla always found it hard fitting in with others. But when his ex wife, Justine Wilson exposed Elon’s secret - Elon’s worst fears came boiling to the surface. He tried to escape into his work, but the dark truth was out. What’s the REAL reason behind Elon Musk’s level of ambition? And what painful lesson was he forced to finally learn?

#Goalcast #Inspiration #Motivation #GoalcastMotivation #GoalcastInspiration #elonmusk #tesla #spacex #teslamotors #elon #science #entrepreneur #JustineMusk #business #technology #Divorce #bloodangel #justinemuskquotes #darksecre
